@1308_21904 @K_G_Andersen @PeterHotez @scrippsresearch Triple-vaxxed and still got breakthrough Omicron (with symptoms, thanks) despite being super careful and upgrading to KN95 when the variant hit.

Still have lingering fatigue and crushing headaches 8 weeks later -- no underlying health issues prior.

That isn't "fine" or "mild".
